39  trajectory_controller_names = ["panda_joint_trajectory_controller"]

51  }

71  def switch_mode(self, desired_mode):
72  """
73  Based on mode type desired by user, switch controllers from current one.
74 
75  Desired mode should be a ControllerType enum
76

84  pass
85  else:
